{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-08", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-08</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> OpenAI's Chief Futurist Is Leaving the Company<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">OpenAI 首席未來學家宣布離職</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Joshua Achiam, who spent nearly nine years at OpenAI researching AI safety, is departing after playing a notable role in the Musk v. Altman trial.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Joshua Achiam 在 OpenAI 任職近九年、專注於 AI 安全研究，曾在馬斯克對奧特曼的訴訟中留下深刻印象，如今宣布離開公司。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Wired</b> · <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/openai-chief-futurist-joshua-achiam-is-leaving-the-company/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> Meta's New Muse Image Model Can Pull Other Instagram Users Into AI Photos<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Meta 推出 Muse 圖像生成模型，Instagram 照片恐被用於 AI 生圖</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Meta's Superintelligence Labs launched its first image model, Muse, now powering image tools across Meta AI, Instagram, and WhatsApp — public Instagram users must opt out to keep their photos from being used.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Meta Superintelligence Labs 推出首款圖像模型 Muse，已進駐 Meta AI、Instagram 與 WhatsApp 的生圖功能，公開帳號用戶須自行選擇退出才能避免照片被使用。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/tech/962485/meta-muse-image-ai-model-instagram\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eef4ff;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#5b8def;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> SCOTUS Lets Texas Enforce App Store Law That Big Tech Calls \"Censorship Regime\"<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#3b6cf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">美國最高法院維持德州應用程式商店年齡驗證法</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The Supreme Court left in place a 5th Circuit ruling allowing Texas to enforce its app store age-verification law, which Big Tech calls a \"censorship regime.\"</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">美國最高法院維持第五巡迴上訴法院判決，讓德州得以持續施行應用程式商店年齡驗證法，科技巨頭稱此舉形同「審查制度」。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Ars Technica</b> · <a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2026/07/supreme-court-lets-texas-enforce-age-verification-law-on-app-stores/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#ecf7ef;border-left:5px solid #4caf72;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#4caf72;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> Microsoft Joins AI Cost-Cutting Trend by Relying More on Its Own Models<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e9e57;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">微軟加入 AI 節流行列，轉為更倚重自家模型</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Microsoft is the latest tech giant to rein in AI spending, shifting toward greater use of its in-house models instead of relying solely on partners.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">微軟成為最新一家縮減 AI 支出的科技巨頭，轉為更倚重自家模型，減少對外部合作夥伴的依賴。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/07/microsoft-joins-ai-cost-cutting-trend-by-relying-more-on-its-own-models/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f1ecfb;border-left:5px solid #8a6bd8;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#8a6bd8;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> Claude Cowork Expands to Mobile and Web<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6b3bf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Claude Cowork 正式推出手機與網頁版</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic's Claude Cowork agent platform is now available on mobile and web, letting users start a task at their desk and pick up the results later, even with their laptop closed.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic 的 Claude Cowork 代理平台正式推出手機與網頁版，使用者可在電腦上啟動任務，之後即使闔上筆電也能隨時查看進度與成果。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/07/the-coding-agent-wars-are-spilling-into-the-rest-of-the-office-claude-cowork/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f6f5;border-left:5px solid #2bb0a6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#2bb0a6;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> Facing US Export Controls, China's DeepSeek Plans to Make Its Own Chips<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#0f9b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">模型</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">面對美國出口管制，中國 DeepSeek 傳計畫自研晶片</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">DeepSeek is reportedly moving to design its own chips to cut its dependence on Nvidia and Huawei amid tightening US export controls.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">面對美國出口管制加劇，中國 DeepSeek 傳出計畫自行研發晶片，以降低對 Nvidia 與華為的依賴。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Ars Technica</b> · <a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/ai/2026/07/facing-us-export-controls-chinas-deepseek-plans-to-make-its-own-chips/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">7.</span> Reddit Is Using LLMs to Solve a Problem LLMs Largely Created<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Reddit 用大型語言模型打擊 AI 垃圾內容</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Reddit is deploying large language models to fight AI-generated spam, fighting fire with fire in the AI era.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Reddit 正利用大型語言模型打擊由 AI 產生的垃圾內容，在 AI 時代以其人之道還治其人之身。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/06/reddit-is-using-llms-to-solve-a-problem-llms-largely-created/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">8.</span> North Korea's Lazarus Launches NPM Supply Chain Attack Disguised as Rollup Tool<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">北韓駭客Lazarus發動NPM供應鏈攻擊，偽裝Rollup工具竊資</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">North Korea's Lazarus Group uploaded a malicious NPM package disguised as a Rollup Polyfill build tool, deploying a multi-stage payload that installs a remote access trojan to steal browser and crypto wallet data.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">北韓駭客組織 Lazarus 於 NPM 上架偽裝成 Rollup Polyfill 建置工具的惡意套件，透過多層次酬載部署遠端存取木馬，竊取瀏覽器與加密貨幣錢包資料。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177138\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#edeefb;border-left:5px solid #6b72d6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#6b72d6;font-weight:800;\">9.</span> Illinois Follows New York and California, Requires Third-Party Audits for Top AI Models<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#5159c9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">伊利諾州跟進紐約與加州，要求頂尖AI模型接受第三方安全稽核</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Illinois Governor JB Pritzker signed the Artificial Intelligence Safety Measures Act, requiring developers of large advanced AI systems to disclose safety measures, report major incidents, and undergo independent audits.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">伊利諾州州長普利茲克簽署《人工智慧安全措施法》，要求大型先進AI系統開發商揭露安全措施、通報重大安全事件，並定期接受獨立第三方安全稽核。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177144\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">10.</span> Claude Cowork Sandbox Flaw Could Let Attackers Gain VM Root Access<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Claude Cowork遭指可被濫用取得VM root權限</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Security researchers at Armadin disclosed that Claude Desktop for Windows' sandbox isolation for Claude Cowork could be abused by an attacker with local code execution to gain root access inside its Ubuntu VM and loosen outbound network restrictions.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">資安團隊 Armadin 揭露，Claude Desktop for Windows 中 Claude Cowork 所用的沙箱隔離機制，可能被已能在本機執行程式的攻擊者濫用，取得虛擬機內的 root 權限並放寬對外連線限制。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177116\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}